| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4929 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ab6db1c3-10c4-57ef-85a5-a5d4c0d51865"
index=*
